Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.13,0:00:46.63,CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}向这丑陋的世界轻声说「再见」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.73,0:00:54.33,CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}用这对朱色翅膀掩去一切丑陋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.93,0:01:06.43,CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,000)}思念如附着的污渍般挥之不去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.53,0:01:10.93,CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}在这地球上生存着的人儿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.03,0:01:18.83,CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}令人窒息般地紧紧相拥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.84,0:01:25.03,CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}凝视着镜中的另一个自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.53,0:01:30.93,CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}为了隐藏自己的软弱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.73,0:01:38.13,CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}去刺伤那些温柔善良的心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.14,0:01:44.63,CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}向这丑陋的世界轻声说「再见」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.73,0:01:50.53,CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}朱色的翅膀轻盈地舞动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.54,0:01:56.93,CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}烈火般的热吻一次次重复着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.94,0:02:09.03,CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}就用这最后一吻收敛起热情奔放的心
Dialogue: 2,0:22:24.64,0:22:31.13,C2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}太阳把热情的目光投向这边
Dialogue: 2,0:22:31.34,0:22:36.53,C2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}真想好好享受这夏天 这阳光
Dialogue: 2,0:22:36.54,0:22:43.93,C2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}今天会发生什么令人激情澎湃的事吗
Dialogue: 2,0:22:44.24,0:22:48.63,C2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}小小的不安点缀着这美妙的期盼
Dialogue: 2,0:22:50.24,0:22:56.03,C2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,200)}夏天的回忆涌现在我脑际
Dialogue: 2,0:22:56.14,0:23:01.93,C2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)}晶亮的碎片注入天空大海充满世界
Dialogue: 2,0:23:02.04,0:23:06.73,C2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,100)}低声私语请求你的拥抱
Dialogue: 2,0:23:06.74,0:23:09.73,C2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}顽皮地挑逗
Dialogue: 2,0:23:09.74,0:23:14.73,C2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}不需要你做出暧昧的温柔
Dialogue: 2,0:23:16.24,0:23:22.63,C2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,000)}那一瞬 我已经预感到一切
Dialogue: 2,0:23:22.64,0:23:26.53,C2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(000,300)}在这热情洋溢的季节
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.43,0:00:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,据说现今存在于地球上的动植物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.93,0:00:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不下400万种
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.63,0:00:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,但是地球诞生以来存在过的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.33,0:00:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,总计可达50亿到500亿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.83,0:00:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是说99.9%的种类
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.23,0:00:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,未能逃脱灭绝的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.63,0:00:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,地球上的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.43,0:00:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,过去共遭受6次大灭绝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.83,0:00:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,但其灭绝原因和过程现在仍然不明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.63,0:02:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我在想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.13,0:02:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,就算我什么都不做
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.53,0:02:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,世界还是照常运作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.63,0:02:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,遥远的某处正在进行的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.73,0:02:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,还是没有要停的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.53,0:02:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,犯罪也无法消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.63,0:02:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,走到哪儿都有讨厌的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.23,0:02:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,即使我做点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.03,0:02:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这个世界也不会因此变好或变坏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.23,0:02:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,所以才躺在这儿无所事事 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.53,0:02:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这也能成为偷懒的借口吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.83,0:02:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.93,0:02:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,痛死了 你们干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.93,0:02:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,世上的事随便它去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.23,0:02:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,竹本健同学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在要做的应该是打扫游泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.23,0:02:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了 我做
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.93,0:03:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,对对 别乱扯谈 要动手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.53,0:03:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那我到那儿的消毒槽...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.23,0:03:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那边是更衣室
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.73,0:03:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你去打扫出口
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.83,0:03:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,健的份我来做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.33,0:03:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,辽少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.73,0:03:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,本来听说游泳部人手不够
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.03,0:03:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,主动要帮忙的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.33,0:03:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,辽少爷 你太体贴了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.13,0:03:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,和竹本完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.33,0:03:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,但是不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.03,0:03:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的两个人总在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.33,0:03:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这一点 我也觉得不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.43,0:03:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那是因为我喜欢健
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.03,0:03:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,当然也包括浴香和樱子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.83,0:03:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,听到了吗 浴香 辽少爷说喜欢我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.63,0:03:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然把我们和健相提并论 有点不服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.93,0:03:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,太遗憾了 辽喜欢人是盲目的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.43,0:03:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.23,0:03:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,人家正高兴的时候泼冷水
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.73,0:03:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你这家伙...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.33,0:03:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.13,0:04:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你小子 碰到这种事就生龙活虎的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.13,0:04:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,他就是这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.03,0:04:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你们 樱子 浴香 健
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.63,0:04:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,认真点干活
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.43,0:04:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.43,0:04:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,第一话 黎明 光与夜的分界线
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.43,0:04:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.33,0:04:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你回来啦 健
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.93,0:04:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,小辽也来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.83,0:04:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.23,0:04:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来了 阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.53,0:04:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.23,0:04:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,叔叔 你又在大白天喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.93,0:04:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么 我每天傍晚都要喝一杯的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.43,0:04:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 你这样店怎么会有发展
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.73,0:04:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你们也喝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.43,0:04:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.33,0:04:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我去洗衣服 你先到房间去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.33,0:04:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.23,0:05:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,麻里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.43,0:05:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,要洗衣服吗 现在麻里正在用浴室
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.33,0:05:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,已经晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.03,0:05:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,就因为这样我才讨厌寄住的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.33,0:05:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,根本不会为人着想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.43,0:05:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道你在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.43,0:05:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,真那么热的话 不会冲个澡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.73,0:05:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚才那样和穿着衣服有什么区别
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.63,0:05:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.13,0:05:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 刚才浴香和樱子打过电话来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.13,0:05:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,说你应该帮忙打扫游泳池的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.73,0:05:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,却玩水玩得忘乎所以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.23,0:05:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,打扫太无聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.63,0:05:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,尽为毫无意义的事拼命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.83,0:05:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不如把那些精力用在其他事上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.93,0:05:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我是健的表妹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.63,0:05:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,连我都会被人抱怨的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.03,0:05:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,辽也好好说说他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.53,0:05:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.63,0:06:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,洗好的衣服我放在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.83,0:06:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,暴风雨总算过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.03,0:06:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,帮你把衣服洗好了 不是很好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.43,0:06:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,亏大了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.73,0:06:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我又不想看她光着身子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.23,0:06:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,还被赏了一巴掌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.33,0:06:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.73,0:06:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,为毫无意义的事拼命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.13,0:06:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.53,0:06:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然明白自己必须做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.53,0:06:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,但不知道该把这种想法用在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.43,0:06:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么搞的 又说到同一个话题了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.83,0:06:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,其实 健是个认真的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.83,0:06:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我 别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.03,0:06:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,健 书包还放在走廊里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.33,0:06:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,快点拿走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.63,0:06:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我周围尽是些唠叨的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.73,0:06:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 我觉得她们都很不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.63,0:06:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.13,0:06:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 健喜欢哪种类型
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.33,0:06:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,干嘛突然问这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.93,0:07:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.03,0:07:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋  比如...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.03,0:07:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,头发比樱子的干爽一点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.53,0:07:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,身材要比浴香好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.43,0:07:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不像麻里那么啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.83,0:07:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你的要求好高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.93,0:07:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.83,0:07:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,素描
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.03,0:07:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,别画 多不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.03,0:07:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.93,0:07:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你画画很棒嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.83,0:07:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,健 健 帮一下忙好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.13,0:07:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.53,0:07:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,薄田的早川先生给“山田印刷”的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.63,0:07:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,5点前送到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.13,0:07:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,发票在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.03,0:07:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.53,0:07:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我拿打工费的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.53,0:07:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我也想在更好的地方开店
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.43,0:07:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,多赚点钱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.43,0:07:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不管怎么样 不能骑得太快哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.03,0:08:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,说到骑得快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.13,0:08:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,上次之后还能动 这个烂铁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.13,0:08:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,所以嘛 不要骑得太快哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.03,0:08:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.83,0:08:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不是要去练弓道嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.43,0:08:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,回来的时候顺便送我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.43,0:08:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,真是个大行李
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.23,0:08:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,健
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.63,0:08:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,路上当心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.03,0:08:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,一直辛苦你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.93,0:08:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,以后也多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.43,0:08:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,真是 叔叔一点上进心也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.43,0:08:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,他大概认为现在这样足够的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.33,0:08:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,就用不着逞强
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.73,0:08:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么不好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.13,0:08:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.63,0:08:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,明明尝试一下会有发展的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.53,0:08:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,闷头向前不一定是正确的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.43,0:08:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,但我喜欢健的这种性格
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.23,0:09:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,看那个 那道光
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.73,0:09:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.73,0:09:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,又回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.73,0:09:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,会不会是流星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.53,0:09:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.43,0:09:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶 到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.33,0:09:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.93,0:09:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,辽 刚才的光你也看到了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.73,0:09:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.73,0:10:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好像有什么东西从脑子里穿过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.93,0:10:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.53,0:10:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那是刚才的光
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.23,0:10:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,是人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.13,0:10:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,健
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.93,0:11:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,光 我是光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.93,0:11:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我是光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.43,0:11:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,是个女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.43,0:12:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.73,0:12:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,辽 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.33,0:12:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,总算把它赶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.73,0:12:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你关键时刻还真能派上用场
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.83,0:13:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这下肯定要挨叔叔骂了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.73,0:13:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,来 把这个穿上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.23,0:13:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你老是光着身子 我们可伤脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.73,0:13:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,明明刚才一直黏在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.53,0:13:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那是没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.03,0:13:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不得不那么做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.83,0:13:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不要闻味道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.53,0:13:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才那家伙说不定会再来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.43,0:13:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,得快点逃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.73,0:13:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你那么说 那这女孩怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.63,0:13:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚才就纳闷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.73,0:13:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这女孩和你白天画的画
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.63,0:13:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.33,0:13:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.53,0:13:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.73,0:13:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是按照健所说的画出来而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.53,0:13:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是健理想中的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.53,0:14:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你的名字叫光吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.43,0:14:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我是光
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.33,0:14:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才在路上遇到的闪光也是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.33,0:14:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你还真能自然地和她对话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.93,0:14:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,光的事 健不想知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.93,0:14:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这个女孩的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.13,0:14:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,为这女孩取名为“光”的是健啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.83,0:14:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,一定是那个时候...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.53,0:14:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我可没那么想过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.13,0:14:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 很好的名字哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.33,0:14:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,只有下决心了 健
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.53,0:14:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,决心 什么决心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.63,0:14:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道 这要看健了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.03,0:14:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.43,0:14:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对是冲着这女孩来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.43,0:14:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不想自找麻烦的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.33,0:14:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,什么决心都不用下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.73,0:14:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这也不失为一种选择
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.93,0:15:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,别怕 只是什么东西掉下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.63,0:15:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,她在发抖 这女孩很不安
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.63,0:15:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,柔软 精致
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.63,0:15:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,光 光
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.73,0:15:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫健 竹本健
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.73,0:15:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,健...健
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.53,0:15:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,别怕 我一定会保护光的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.43,0:15:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,健
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.83,0:15:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 健
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.43,0:16:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才怎么了 心脏好像要跳出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.13,0:16:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,虫的声音消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.53,0:16:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,辽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.73,0:16:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,健
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.03,0:16:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,放开光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.73,0:16:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,听到没 放开
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.03,0:16:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,健 健
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.43,0:16:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,健
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.13,0:16:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.83,0:16:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,快逃 光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.33,0:16:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我的身体不听使唤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.83,0:16:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你能逃走就好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.63,0:17:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 健
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.43,0:17:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.03,0:17:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.93,0:17:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,光
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.93,0:17:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.43,0:17:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋 说了要保护她的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.73,0:17:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么都做不了吗 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.53,0:17:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.13,0:18:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.13,0:18:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,等着我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.03,0:18:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,健
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.23,0:18:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.23,0:18:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,从身体最深处涌上来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.03,0:18:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这股力量...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.63,0:18:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,正合我意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.03,0:19:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.73,0:19:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,变成这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.53,0:19:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,使用这种力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.43,0:19:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不分青红皂白 横冲乱撞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.83,0:19:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,够了 已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.23,0:19:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.33,0:20:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,等...等等
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.33,0:20:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.23,0:20:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,有股我最喜欢的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.73,0:20:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,对 你快要死了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.13,0:20:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,光　 辽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.33,0:21:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.03,0:21:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,辽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.73,0:21:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,健
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.83,0:21:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,光 光
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.13,0:21:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,健
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.43,0:21:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,光 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.53,0:21:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,健
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.63,0:21:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,光
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.13,0:21:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,没事了 我会保护光的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.53,0:21:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.83,0:21:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这里到底发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.03,0:21:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,因为怪物的血而闪着蓝光的河边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.93,0:21:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我许下了誓言 我要保护光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.93,0:22:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一个满月的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.03,0:22:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,于是一切从这里开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.03,0:23:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我是西野麻里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.73,0:23:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.73,0:23:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是金鱼什么的也就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.03,0:23:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是失去父母的小猫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.43,0:23:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,就当作没看见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.53,0:23:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,可是健这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.13,0:23:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,偏偏把一个来历不明的女孩带回来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.73,0:24:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,还说“我要保护这个女孩”
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.93,0:24:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,下回 这个丑与美的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.83,0:24:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你是第一个
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.63,0:24:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,什么 什么第一个
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.03,0:24:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,如果真是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.33,0:24:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不放过你
